1. *Smiri* se i oslobodi stresa! (Calm down and relieve the stress!)
2. Ona je uspela da *smiri* situaciju. (She managed to calm down the situation.)
3. Uspela je da mu *smiri* razdraženost. (She managed to calm down his agitation.)
4. On je vikao da *smiri* decu. (He was yelling to calm the children down.)
5. On je pokušao da *smiri* situaciju. (He tried to calm down the situation.)